<!---------------------------->
<table cellpadding=2 cellspacing=2>
<tr><td valign="top"><b>Recommended Level<br>for starting quest:</b></td><td valign="bottom"> 50<br></td></tr>
<tr><td valign="top"><b>Starting zone:</b></td><td valign="top"> East Cabilis<br></td></tr>
<tr><td valign="top"><b>Additional zones:</b></td><td valign="top"> Kaesora, City of Mist, Mistmoore, Temple of Droga<br></td></tr>
<tr><td valign="top"><b>Starting NPC:</b></td><td valign="top"> Arch Duke Xog<br></td></tr>
<tr><td valign="top"><b>Reward:</b></td><td valign="top"> Lord of Pain's Khukri<br><br></td></tr>
</table>

This is the last step before you actually strive for the Greenmist itself, if you want the text, find it elsewhere, here is how you get it.<br>
<br>
Make sure you have the Hero's Khukri, first.  Then find 6 illegible scrolls.  The first can be found in Kaesora from a Failed Crypt Raider.  Number 2, 3, and 4 all drop randomly from the Spectral Courier in the Stable area of City of Mist.  Scroll 5 drops from a dark librarian in Mistmoore.  And Scroll 6 is dropped by the <i>assistant</i> dark librarian, also in Mistmoore.<br>
<br>
Take these 6 scrolls and go to the Temple of Droga.  Go to the jail area of Droga and kill goblin penmasters and goblin penkeepers until you have obtained 4 different keys (bone key, bone key necklace, stone key, bronze key).  Take these keys, and wait for an Iksar to spawn wearing gold chain armor in the daytime.  Hand him the 4 keys and he'll give you an item used to operate the pottery wheel looking thing near the jail area.<br>
<br>
Take the 6 scrolls and the dagger type thing that Argest (the prisoner) gave you and combine them in the aforementioned contraption.  The result is a Stupendous Tome.<br>
<br>
When you give the Stupendous Tome and your Hero's Khukri to Arch Duke Xog, he will give you the Lord of Pain's Khukri, only the Greenmist remains.<br>
<br>
LORE ITEM MAGIC ITEM NO DROP  <br>
Damage: 12<br>
Delay: 24 <br>
Ratio: 2 <br> 
Str: +5 Wis: +5 Int: +10 Magic Resist: +25  <br>
Weight: 4.0 <br>
Weapon Skill: One Hand Slash <br>
Class: Shadowknight  <br>
Race: Iksar  
<br>

